## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the scope of perspectives included. Some sources may present biased views, particularly opinion pieces and social media posts. Additionally, the complexity of homelessness as a social issue means that not all aspects could be covered comprehensively in this report. Further research could include more diverse perspectives and recent data to provide a more holistic view.

